"{\"uid\": \"espn.com-olympics-story-_-id-40625418-2024-olympic-opening-ceremony-outfits-usa-haiti-mongolia-chinese-taipei\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Theopening ceremonyfor the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris offers the world's top athletes a moment to shine well before any podium appearances.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 51, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.511359668494652e-34, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike most of the upcoming Olympic events, gold, silver, and bronze will not be the highlights on Friday.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Olympians will proudly wear denim, cashmere, cotton, and other fabrics in their opening ceremony uniforms.\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, these ensembles highlight the intersection of fashion and sports, offering a global stage for cultural expression and unity.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are some must-see opening ceremony uniforms from around the world:  Designer: Ralph Lauren  America is renowned for its red, white, and blue, but this time the spotlight is on the blue.\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9999999747496989, \"rank\": 2.5250020167432352e-08, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nation's athletes will don navy blazers, striped button-up shirts, and denim jeans.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"denim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\"}, {\"begin\": 776, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"jeans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These blazers are adorned with patriotic trim and display the Olympic logo.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Ralph Lauren (@ralphlauren)  Designer: Sportscraft  The country's national colors of green and gold provide the base shades for the ensemble.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9999999747496989, \"rank\": 2.5250020167432352e-08, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both men and women will wear a green linen blazer paired with stone-colored shorts or a green and gold ombre pleated skirt.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The blazer features the Australian Olympians' Oath, on the inside jacket pocket and the names of all 301 Australian Summer Olympic champions are inscribed on the jacket lining.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9995760908382048, \"rank\": 0.00042408860031183093, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9995760908382048, \"rank\": 0.00042408860031183093, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The story behind our tenth@SportscraftAustralian Olympic Team Opening Ceremony uniform accompanied by@VolleyAustraliafootwear \\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9b\\ud83c\\udde6\\ud83c\\uddfa \\ud83c\\uddeb\\ud83c\\uddf7Bring on 26 July, 2024.\\ud83d\\udc49https://t.co/M9JrnxCMuZ#AllezAUSpic.twitter.com/Yojqh17Zw4  \\ud83d\\udc9a Goosebumps \\ud83d\\udc9b For an athlete there is nothing like putting on the Australian Olympic Team jacket.#AllezAUS|@Sportscraft|@VolleyAustralia|@WaterPoloAus|@AusVolley|@Paddle_Auspic.twitter.com/B6sH9eGm2p  This morning we launched into 1\\ufe0f\\u20e30\\ufe0f\\u20e30\\ufe0f\\u20e3 days to#Paris2024by revealing the Australian Olympic Team Opening Ceremony uniform at the stunning Clovelly Beach in Sydney \\ud83c\\udde6\\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9b#AllezAUS|@Sportscraft|@VolleyAustraliapic.twitter.com/241iuj2OzW  Designer: Lululemon  Thanks to Lululemon, Canadian athletes will not have to choose between style and comfort.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.482249695656834e-20, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1825, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.482249695656834e-20, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1849, \"end\": 1865, 