\\\"Mountain Range of Taiwan\\\" painting.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2361, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.104385283058737e-16, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2514, \"end\": 2525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"score\": 0.9999911657204444, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Chou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\"}, {\"begin\": 2514, \"end\": 2525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"score\": 0.9999911657204444, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Chou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It further pays homage to the country by highlighting its national flowers and traditional good luck tokens.\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by JUST IN XX (@justinxx_official)  Designer: Alpine Pro  The Czech Republic's Olympic opening ceremony attire draws inspiration from its national flag, which consists of two horizontal stripes of white over red with a blue triangle at the hoist.\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Underneath the white and blue outer layer is a polo shirt featuring a gradient design of all three national shades, complemented by blue slacks.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by C\\u030cesky\\u0301 olympijsky\\u0301 ty\\u0301m \\ud83c\\udde8\\ud83c\\uddff (@olympijskytym)  Designer: Berluti  Men and women of the host country will wear tailored midnight-blue tuxedo jackets and matching pants (or option of a wrap skirt for women)  paired with white button-up shirts.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Inside each item, the phrase \\\"Artisan of all victories\\\" is embroidered on a label with gold thread.\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ensemble will be accessorized with patterned pocket handkerchiefs, scarves, and hand-varnished belts, along with lapel pins in blue and red, reflecting the key colors of the French flag.\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[#Paris2024]M\\u00e9lina Robert-Michon, Florent Manaudou, Nantenin Keita et Alexis Hanquinquant ont \\u00e9t\\u00e9 choisis par leurs pairs pour repr\\u00e9senter la France lors des Jeux Olympiques et Paralympiques de Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3712, \"end\": 3714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hash_(EP)\", \"score\": 0.9999999947203833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"[#\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hash_(EP)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hash_(EP)\"}, {\"begin\": 3724, \"end\": 3744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999454303, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"M\\u00e9lina Robert-Michon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\"}, {\"begin\": 3724, \"end\": 3744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999454303, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"M\\u00e9lina Robert-Michon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\"}, {\"begin\": 3746, \"end\": 3753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\", \"score\": 0.9999927870127089, \"rank\": 7.213039265074097e-06, \"text\": \"Florent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Les athl\\u00e8tes ont exprim\\u00e9 leur joie et l'honneur que cela repr\\u00e9sente...pic.twitter.com/29UI2kyYLZ  Designer: Ben Sherman  For the opening ceremony, Team Great Britain will don a white bomber jacket with navy sleeves, adorned with a floral embroidery on the back.\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 4160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3931, \"end\": 3934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"score\": 0.9999999999654392, \"rank\": 3.411511736282896e-11, \"text\": \"ont\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\"}, {\"begin\": 4101, \"end\": 4114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flight_jacket\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"bomber jacket\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flight_jacket\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flight_jacket\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This design, incorporating the rose, thistle, daffodil, and shamrock, symbolizes the unity of the United Kingdom's four nations of \\u200b\\u200bEngland, Scotland, Wales, and Northern Ireland.\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4313, \"end\": 4320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"score\": 0.9999972026656013, \"rank\": 2.5267471011370605e-06, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\"}, {\"begin\": 4322, \"end\": 4330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999481588, \"rank\": 4.819264676679447e-11, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\"}, {\"begin\": 4332, \"end\": 4337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.9999998900339111, \"rank\": 1.0576208375009078e-07, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ensemble will be completed with a knitted polo that bears a geometric red-and-blue pattern and light blue trousers.\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Opening Ceremony wear features tailored pieces for all athletes representing Team GB, including a bomber style jacket.On the back of the jacket is a specially designed and embroidered four-nation floral design.pic.twitter.com/r4vkF4N5Om  Designer: Jaspe  Guatemala's design features a vibrant palette of green and blue.\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Women will wear green dresses paired with blue vests, while men will sport blue button-up shirts and green slacks.\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To complete the look, both ensembles are accessorized with blue hats and black shoulder pads adorned with colorful traditional prints.\", \"from\": 4902, \"to\": 5036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83e\\udd29 Presentamos la indumentaria que portar\\u00e1n nuestros atletas en la ceremonia de inauguraci\\u00f3n de los Juegos Ol\\u00edmpicos de#Par\\u00eds2024\\ud83c\\uddeb\\ud83c\\uddf7, dise\\u00f1ada para representar la fuerza, la resiliencia y la belleza de nuestro pa\\u00eds.\\u00a1Con orgullo, con valent\\u00eda, con Guatemala en el alma!\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5218, \"end\": 5227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Fuerza\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"la fuerza\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Fuerza\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Fuerza\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\udc99\\ud83e\\udd0dpic.twitter.com/N86pwMCAZL  Designer: Stella Jean  Local artist Philippe Dodard's \\\"Passage\\\" painting takes center stage in the uniform's skirt and trousers with a dynamic print.\", \"from\": 5305, \"to\": 5484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5305, \"end\": 5314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\", \"score\": 0.9999999996252882, \"rank\": 3.7434126981475894e-10, \"text\": \"Guatemala\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\"}, {\"begin\": 5321, \"end\": 5325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\", \"score\": 0.9999959485303624, \"rank\": 4.045204422168767e-06, \"text\": \"alma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\"}, {\"begin\": 5369, \"end\": 5380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stella Jean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women will complement the vibrant pattern with a woven shirt and belted blazer.\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Men, on the other hand, will wear light bluefield jackets inspired by the classic Haitian Guayabera shirt.\", \"from\": 5569, \"to\": 5675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Stella Jean (@stellajean_sj_)  Designer: Laura Weber  Ireland's all-white outfits celebrate the country's century-long participation in the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5718, \"end\": 5729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stella Jean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each athlete's jacket includes a distinctive embroidered patch on the sleeve, showcasing a beaded, sequined, and stone-studded design of the athlete.\", \"from\": 5850, \"to\": 5999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a symbol of good luck, the jackets also feature a shamrock brooch crafted from four embroidered four-leaf clovers.\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TEAM IRELAND OPENING CEREMONY WEARIrish designed, made, and worn for the@paris2024Olympic Opening Ceremony in one week \\ud83e\\udd47Team Ireland x Laura Weber#TeamIreland|#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/J9rldrojx8  Designer: Unknown  Kazakhstani athletes will sport white shirts with ties beneath striking blue blazers, complemented by white skirts or trousers.\", \"from\": 6119, \"to\": 6462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adorning the bottom of the blazers and the sides of the pants are a series of symbols, each rich with historical significance.\", \"from\": 6463, \"to\": 6589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the illustrative elements are \\\"m\\u00fcyiz\\\" (horns), embodying strength, courage, and protection, while \\\"kaz moiyn\\\" (gooseneck) captures the essence of flexibility, agility, and grace.\", \"from\": 6590, \"to\": 6774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Traditional ceremony of presenting the State Flag of the Republic of Kazakhstan to the Olympic team \\ud83c\\uddf0\\ud83c\\uddffSee you soon, Paris!\", \"from\": 6776, \"to\": 6898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6858, \"end\": 6866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.997929250526957, \"rank\": 0.001402928965334617, \"text\": \"Republic\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@olympic_kzpic.twitter.com/wPaNSUHaAl  Designer: Unknown  Malaysia's opening ceremony uniforms honor the Malayan tiger, the country's national animal.\", \"from\": 6898, \"to\": 7048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6994, \"end\": 7010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 2.9254897598660025e-13, \"text\": \"opening ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The jacket proudly displays an eye-catching print of orange and black stripes, echoing the tiger's majestic appearance.\", \"from\": 7049, \"to\": 7168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ensemble is finished off with sleek black pants.\", \"from\": 7169, \"to\": 7221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"https://t.co/LeJ62UedVWpic.twitter.com/Pypuj6laVI  Designer: Men's Fashion  The Mexican Olympic team will don a striking pink and white outfit featuring sleeve prints inspired by the cities of Oaxaca, San Miguel de Allende, and Michoac\\u00e1n.\", \"from\": 7223, \"to\": 7461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7443, \"end\": 7449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\", \"score\": 0.9984603825971633, \"rank\": 0.0015419914794168575, \"text\": \"Oaxaca\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\"}, {\"begin\": 7451, \"end\": 7472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Miguel_de_Allende\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.062259411333432e-46, \"text\": \"San Miguel de Allende\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Miguel_de_Allende\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Miguel_de_Allende\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The black t-shirt underneath the jacket is meant to pay homage to El \\u00c1ngel, a monument that commemorates Mexico's War of Independence centennial.\", \"from\": 7462, \"to\": 7607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Men's Fashion (@mensfashionoficial)  Designer: Michel & Amazonka  The ivory-colored ceremonial garments pay homage to the Mongolian deel, a classic calf-length tunic.\", \"from\": 7609, \"to\": 7792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elements such as the Soyombo symbol and the mythological Gua-Maral deer are intricately woven into the vest's gold stitching.\", \"from\": 7793, \"to\": 7918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7813, \"end\": 7818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tunic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0483712193064696e-70, \"text\": \"tunic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tunic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tunic\"}, {\"begin\": 7841, \"end\": 7855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soyombo_symbol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Soyombo symbol\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soyombo_symbol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soyombo_symbol\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the designers, each outfit took around 20 hours to craft.\", \"from\": 7920, \"to\": 7990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Michel&Amazonka (@michelamazonka)  Designer: Munisa Standard  Inspired by the national \\\"taegeuk\\\" circular symbol, the uniforms also incorporate the meaning of one of the black trigrams from the flag, symbolizing water.\", \"from\": 7992, \"to\": 8227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Korea's light-blue look features a blazer with a lining engraved with traditional white and blue porcelain designs, paired with a belt and slacks.\", \"from\": 8229, \"to\": 8381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8230, \"end\": 8234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9780049512219632, \"rank\": 0.022489711069837326, \"text\": \"flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\